"title": "5367: kingdoms",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5367",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Realms or reigns of kings. The kingdoms of this world have power under the sovereignty of God. They are ultimately judged by God and will be superseded by the kingdom of God. The phrase “the kingdom of the air” is used to describe the spiritual realm in which Satan operates.</p>\n<h2>Israel and the kingdoms around her</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:21\">1KI 4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:21-Deut3:22\">DEU 3:21–3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:25\">DEU 28:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:10\">JOS 11:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:20-Judg3:4\">JDG 2:20–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:18\">1SA 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:10\">2CH 17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:29\">2CH 20:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:22\">NEH 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer34:1\">JER 34:1</a></p>\n<h2>The kingdoms of this world</h2>\n<h3>God is sovereign over the kingdoms of this world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:15\">2KI 19:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:16\">ISA 37:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:1\">2KI 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:19\">2KI 19:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:6\">2CH 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:23\">2CH 36:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:2\">EZR 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:6\">PSA 46:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:1\">PRO 21:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:1\">ISA 45:1</a></p>\n<h3>The kingdoms of this world will honour and worship God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:21-Ps102:22\">PSA 102:21–102:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:32\">PSA 68:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:24-Rev21:26\">REV 21:24–21:26</a></p>\n<h3>Under the sovereignty of God a succession of kingdoms will rule the earth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:36-Dan2:43\">DAN 2:36–2:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:17\">DAN 7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:23-Dan7:25\">DAN 7:23–7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:19-Dan8:22\">DAN 8:19–8:22</a></p>\n<h3>The kingdom of God will supersede and be greater than the kingdoms of this world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:15\">REV 11:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:44-Dan2:45\">DAN 2:44–2:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:26\">DAN 6:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13-Dan7:14\">DAN 7:13–7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:18\">DAN 7:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:27\">DAN 7:27</a></p>\n<h3>God's judgment on the kingdoms of this world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:8\">ZEP 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:6\">PSA 79:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:10-Isa10:11\">ISA 10:10–10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:19\">ISA 13:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:8\">JER 28:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:26\">DAN 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:22\">HAG 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:15-Rev6:17\">REV 6:15–6:17</a></p>\n<h3>God's people will be given sovereignty over the kingdoms of this world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:27\">DAN 7:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:10\">JER 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:26-Rev2:27\">REV 2:26–2:27</a></p>\n<h3>In this world God enables his people to overcome ``kingdoms'' by faith</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:32-Heb11:33\">HEB 11:32–11:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:4\">1JN 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>The devil tempts Jesus Christ by offering him the kingdoms of this world if he will worship him</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:8-Matt4:10\">MAT 4:8–4:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:5-Luke4:8\">LUK 4:5–4:8</a></p>\n<h2>The kingdom of the air</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:2\">EPH 2:1–2:2</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The kingdom of Satan</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:26\">MAT 12:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:18\">LUK 11:18</a></p>\n<h2>The kingdoms of the sea</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:11\">ISA 23:11</a> <em>The Phoenicians, who were great sailors, appeared to have dominion over the sea (see <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:1-Isa23:4\">Isa 23:1–4</a>), but in reality it belongs to God.</em></p>",
